sentences: She was the vocalist for the band Machine Gun Fellatio (as KK Juggy) from 2000 to 2005.
Alongside her solo career, Hughes was also the Ring Mistress with Circus Oz (2006–08) and has issued an album, 21st Century Blues (2010) with her father.
